data.description: Step inside this charming 3 bedroom+den, 2 bathroom haven nestled on 2.27 acres. From the moment you pass through the gate, you'll be captivated by the inviting allure of this home. As you make your way indoors, the heart of this home opens before you-a spacious great room designed for memory-making gatherings. While the family chef works their culinary magic in the open kitchen, guests gather around the island, sharing stories & laughter. And when it's time for those cherished holiday meals, the formal dining room beckons. At the end of each day, retreat to your main bedroom, a true sanctuary complete with 2 walk-in closets. Your private en suite bathroom is a luxurious escape, featuring dual sinks, a private water closet, a beautifully tiled shower, & a separate soaking tub. The guest rooms offer a peaceful respite, situated apart from the main suite. They share a generously sized bathroom with a tub/shower combination. This home boasts an array of thoughtfully chosen upgrades like wood cabinetry, granite countertops, upgraded tile flooring, stainless steel appliances, & impact-resistant doors & windows. This property enjoys a prime spot, close to schools, shopping, & dining.
